  <name>OrpheusDL GUI</name>
  <summary>Graphical Interface for OrpheusDL</summary>
  <developer id="com.github.orpheusdl">
    <name>Bas Curtiz</name>
  </developer>
  <description>
    <p>
      Makes downloading music with OrpheusDL easy on Windows, macOS, and Linux. 
      Search multiple platforms and download high-quality audio with complete metadata.
    </p>
    <p>Key Features:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Cross-platform support (Windows, macOS, Linux) with easy installation</li>
      <li>Thoughtful and modern graphical user interface</li>
      <li>Supports all major platforms: Apple Music, Beatport, Beatsource, Deezer, Qobuz, SoundCloud, Spotify, Tidal, YouTube</li>
      <li>Unified search across all platforms or individual search by type (track, album, playlist, artist, label)</li>
      <li>Search and explore Dolby Atmos releases on Tidal</li>
      <li>Search by label on Beatport and Beatsource</li>
      <li>Advanced downloading: batch downloads (using text-file input), specific track selection, and quality options per download</li>
      <li>Context menu integration for quick actions and source links</li>
      <li>Concurrent or sequential download modes</li>
      <li>Integrated audio player for previews</li>
      <li>Comprehensive artwork support: cover thumbnails, full-size artwork view, and save/copy options</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
